title: demonmaestro
author: demonmaestro
content: Hows everyone been doing? Been awhile since I got on here.I wonder if any folks that was around since the beginning is still here?!

comments.author: DeathAngel
comments.body: I see you have a 2013 registration, I was 2015. There are many older members still around the forum. Obviously theymos is still active, OgNasty is still around. I hope bitcoin changed your life & brought you some level of financial freedom. It has for me & I was 2 years later than you to the party.
